<br>
About nukes:<br>
- more damages regarding to the skill (not sure, we have focus and crits)<br>
- less mana regarding to the skill (OK and already the case)<br>
- faster cast (not OK, we already get focus for that, and AA for few spells)<br>
- I will add RESIST CHECK<br>
<br>
Now, i'm not sure if the skill sould add to the initial spell power or simply allow you to use the full spell power...... It's all about 2 philosophic way of thinking :<br>
- spe is here to improve your base power (actual use)<br>
OR<br>
- spe is here to allow you to use the full power of your path (i like this idea, even if i will be flame. It's also really RP)  <p><b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4257">
