Make it that those summons get a boost on all aspects ... and we finally have an alt exp class skill that is worth the effort. Might also be in three levels. That would be 18 alt exp points I would like to spend if the boosts are nice and usefull.<br>
<br>
Could be an ATK, AC, HP boost combined with an upped haste cap and additional add of haste. Maybe like this:<br>
<br>
level 1 (3 points): +150 HP, + 30 ATK, + 25 AC (hastecap upped and haste added 10%)<br>
level 2 (6 points): +300 HP, + 60 ATK, + 50 AC (hastecap upped and haste added 20%)<br>
level 3 (9 points): +600 HP, +120 ATK, + 100 AC (hastecap upped and haste added 30%)<br>
<br>
It works like a buff, holds 15 mins (and refreshes in 15 mins). There is such a line for all pets (water, fire, earth, air) maybe. And maybe the buffs given to each form of pet vary a bit. I wont be much upset if they kicked the actual elelemntal forms out for this ...<br>
